name: Sai sai Catarina
lyrics:
Sai sai Catarina
Saia do mar venha ver Idalina
Sai sai Catarina
Catarina venha ver
Sai sai Catarina
Saia do mar, saia do mar
Sai sai Catarina
Oh Catarina, meu amor
Sai sai Catarina

translations.text:
Come out, come out Catarina
Come out of the sea, come see Idalina
Come out, come out Catarina
Catarina, come see
Come out, come out Catarina
Come out of the sea, come out of the sea
Come out, come out Catarina
Oh Caterina, my love
Come out, come out Catarina
